rule.value:
Local rules and regulations require you to submit your legal name. In addition, please make sure to follow these guidelines:

What am I allowed to enter?
 • All letters from A-Z, including Ñ and their lowercase versions
 • Dashes, periods, and spaces
 • Up to three consecutive i’s (i.e., III) with spaces before and after

What’s not allowed?
 • Numbers and special characters (e.g., 104@!$%çéß)
 • Characters from non-English languages (e.g., Japanese, Greek)
 • Letters repeated 3 or more times consecutively (e.g., AAA, BBB, CCC)
rule.validationMessage: Only letters, dashes and apostrophes are allowed
